    Finally, the system is incapable of resolving plural references to collections of objects introduced by singular NPs, even when these collections were introduced by coordinated noun phrases.
    Although it would be relatively easy to add rules for handling the simplest cases (possibly at the expense of a decrease in precision), many of these references can only be resolved by means of nontrivial operations.
